    <item>
      <title>美联储四年来首次降息，信贷风险指标有所下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/credit-risk-gauge-eases-as-fed-cuts-for-first-time-in-4-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦公开市场委员会 (FOMC) 为实现美国经济罕见的软着陆而降息之后，衡量美国公司债券市场风险的一项关键指标周三小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/credit-risk-gauge-eases-as-fed-cuts-for-first-time-in-4-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:31:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储选择降息半个百分点，交易员押注进一步宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/traders-bet-on-more-easing-as-fed-opts-for-half-point-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储将基准利率下调半个基点并暗示今年将进一步降息后，交易员加大了对美国未来降息步伐的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/traders-bet-on-more-easing-as-fed-opts-for-half-point-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩传呼机爆炸痕迹延伸至台湾、匈牙利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/trail-of-exploding-pagers-in-lebanon-leads-to-taiwan-hungary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星期二下午 3 点 30 分左右，黎巴嫩传呼机爆炸，造成数千人死亡或致残，并引发人们对中东爆发新战争的担忧，爆炸地点就在布达佩斯一条高速公路和一座破旧火车站之间的一间小邮局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/trail-of-exploding-pagers-in-lebanon-leads-to-taiwan-hungary</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 17:42:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储采取重大举措后，股票交易员“抛售新闻”：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储在将利率下调半个百分点后暗示并不急于放松政策，因此股市的上涨一度推动其升至历史新高，但随后遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 22:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
